    <string name="omelette_details">INGREDIENTS:\n• 3 eggs\n• 50ml milk\n• Salt, pepper\n• Butter\n\nSTEPS:\n1. Beat eggs with milk\n2. Add salt and pepper\n3. Fry in butter\n4. Serve hot</string>

    <string name="borscht_details">INGREDIENTS:\n• 500g beef\n• 3 beets\n• 2 carrots\n• 1 onion\n• Cabbage\n• Tomato paste\n\nSTEPS:\n1. Cook broth\n2. Fry vegetables\n3. Add cabbage\n4. Cook until ready\n5. Serve with sour cream</string>

    <string name="pasta_details">INGREDIENTS:\n• 400g pasta\n• 200g bacon\n• 3 eggs\n• Parmesan cheese\n• Black pepper\n\nSTEPS:\n1. Cook pasta\n2. Fry bacon\n3. Mix eggs with cheese\n4. Combine all\n5. Add pepper and serve</string>

